description	"Rebel Vanguard

Class Summary:
A multi-life soldier with single-use rocket, specialty grenades and an evasive roll.

Weaponry:
- Pistol (2)
- DH-17 (3)
- MiniMag PTL Rocket Launcher (1)
- Sonic Detonators (1)
- Concussion Grenade (1)

Attributes:
- Reinforcements (2)
- Dodge (1) (Activates simultaneously with Sprint)
- Assemble

Abilities:
- Stamina (2)
- Dexterity (1) (Can perform evasive rolls with Class Ability 2)

The men and women of the Rebel Alliance were fiercely dedicated to the principle of freedom, and would lay down their lives to win their objectives. Rebel Vanguards were specialized in using heavy weaponry on the battlefield."